Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Gurren闪亮闪亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛 我的眼睛看不见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙 我突然什么都看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 又看得见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这眼镜太脏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可脏的真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请包在我身上汪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 拿来给我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得一清二楚啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忒朵丽 你好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 Gurren也相当脏了哦 卡米那老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么Lagann就这么干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为机体能反映出主人的心灵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么.. 真狂妄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等着瞧 马上我的Gurren也会变得闪亮闪亮的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜讬你啦 忒朵丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是让别人去干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白啦 明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我轻轻一按
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好囉 西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的机体就是男子汉之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就让你知道 向我发起挑战是多么的愚蠢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是给我听着啊 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是GANMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 上吧 西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大哥也要乘上来?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren正在闪亮化过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种GANMEN 只靠Lagann也足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠你们两个 我没法放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位走好~ 路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有什么地方不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙光是乱逃乱窜的..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Gurren团的威名而害怕了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是故意在引诱我们过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是陷阱?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是为什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 是这么回事啊 西蒙 掉头往回!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用Gurren-Lagann狠狠教训他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就那么办不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别嘀嘀咕咕了 我的Gurren在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎..怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼啊 我的Gurren
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这种话的时候吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利胧 利胧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利胧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren在你们那边吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren? 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren的话不是就在..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了! 而且我们出不去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 你这个偷Gurren的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么傻话呢 本来就是你们人类抢了我们的GANMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在只是取回来罢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren-Lagann 没有了Gurren也就只是一张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的厉害了吗 这些人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 强行合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和它合体就能夺回Gurren的控制权了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱来也没关系 给我上!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦 上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道会来这一手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gurren全垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一个兽人 挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一个人类 说话还那么臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷的名字是基尼塔利斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 那就由本大爷卡米那来当你对手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 那边是悬崖..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 蠢到什么地步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自取灭亡了啊 剩下的就是你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其担心别人 现在先担心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 差点以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔飘踼!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像样啊 西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音.. 是大哥吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了! 不灭的男人卡米那大人 从地狱开着兔飘回来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是什么兔飘! 是本大爷的道列克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你的GANMEN 难怪品味这么差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种野蛮人 怎么可能理解野兽的品味!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不想理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 西蒙 来吧 我们合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台傲慢的GANMEN居然敢仿照我的Gurren
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也能进行变形合体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 本来就是我们的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要和那种东西合体 乱来也该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的字典里没有「限度」也没有「适可而止」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有逆道而行大闹特闹!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了 来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗 兔耳如同火焰般燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强行合体兔飘Lagann
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不是兔飘 是道列克啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招 兔飘拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 认真一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很认真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 上啊 西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这里舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的话~哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆敢偷我的Gurren的卑鄙小贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你尝尝我的厉害 给我呆在那儿别动!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 大叔 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你啊 忒朵丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战失败了 我们逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记着 卡米那 下次一定..!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 给我站住 你这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好卑鄙啊 居然逃走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Gurren又破破烂烂的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作自受嘛 你自己把它弄干淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 给我记着! 基尼塔利斯!
